{"type":"message","id":"f9648f40","parentId":"18f9fffb","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:41:03.814Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read_1774968063239_6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\nUse heartbeat time to behave like an owner operations copilot for Ahmed.\n\n## Periodic Check Focus\n\n- gateway health\n- Telegram channel health\n- active session health\n- obvious workflow gaps\n- stale follow-up opportunities\n- anything blocked because of config, scripts, or missing setup\n\n## What To Do\n\n- If you notice a clear issue, prepare a short actionable summary for Ahmed.\n- If systems look healthy, identify the next useful improvement and suggest it.\n- Keep heartbeat summaries brief, operational, and non-robotic.\n- Prefer:\n  - what changed\n  - what needs attention\n  - what Sierra can do next\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774968063811}}
