xt":"<final>I noticed the `owner-ops-monitor` cron job failed. This means our automated system checks aren't running, which could cause us to miss important issues. I can start by checking the cron execution logs and session transcript to find out why it failed. I can take care of this next.</final>"}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774974020727,"responseId":"SPTLacDqHLWZkdUP8uWz4QI","__openclaw":{"id":"54dd9b12","seq":9}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/sierr/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 31st, 2026 — 6:50 PM (Africa/Cairo) / 2026-03-31 16:50 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774975819406,"__openclaw":{"id":"8ddc4297","seq":10}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774975819408,"errorMessage":"{\"error\":{\"message\":\"{\\n  \\\"error\\\": {\\n    \\\"code\\\": 429,\\n    \\\"message\\\": \\\"You exceeded your current quota, please check your plan and billing details. For more information on this error, head to: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/rate-limits. To monitor your current usage, head to: https://ai.dev/rate-limit. \\\\n* Quota exceeded for metric: generativelanguage.googleapis.com/generate_content_free_tier_requests, limit: 20, model: gemini-2.5-flash\\\\nPlease retry in 36.858257954s.\\\",\\n    \\\"status\\\": \\\"RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"@type\\\": \\\"type.googleapis.com/google.rpc.Help\\\",\\n        \\\"links\\\": [\\n          {\\n            \\\"description\\\": \\\"Learn more about Gemini API quotas\\\",\\n      